schema.description: This view aggregates billing data from S4HANA, joining data from VBRK, VBRP, and PRCD_ELEMENTS tables.  It provides a detailed view of billing documents, including customer information, billing items, and rebates, at the billing item level.  The data is further enriched with calendar date dimensions and currency conversion (optional).

formula.value: COUNT(VBRK.VBELN) OVER (PARTITION BY CalendarDateDimension_FKDAT.CalYear, CalendarDateDimension_FKDAT.CalMonth, CalendarDateDimension_FKDAT.CalWeek)
